{"tid":2000651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屈臣氏 : 蒸餾水廠生產WatsMask自家口罩 5月中推出","createTime":"2020-05-04T04:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T06:58:37.000Z","uid":164435,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"2867451a16ad5b12ab68cd3814f4a9d0e7eae066","tid":2000651,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:20:40.000Z","msg":"屈臣氏蒸餾水陪住香港人成長，堅持的是一份We Care精神，無論係缺乏安全食水，定係大家都戰兢地為自己同家人健康擔憂嘅時候，我哋都用心將最好的帶俾大家，同香港人一齊度過每個難關。<br />\n<br />\n為咗呢份初心，我哋短時間內突破性咁將部分蒸餾水廠房，改建成符合ISO 14644-1 Class 8 設施標準嘅「口罩生產無塵車間」，為香港人生產供不應求嘅防護口罩，同屈臣氏蒸餾水一樣，為香港人帶嚟有信心保證、可安心使用嘅優質產品。想知WatsMask WeCare 嘅生產過程？即刻同屈仔去片睇下啦！<br />\n<br />\n屈臣氏自家品牌口罩WatsMask WeCare採用3層過濾防護設計，獨立包裝，經 SGS 測試符合 B.F.E 及 P.F.E 細菌過濾率及顆粒過濾率 &ge;99%，預計五月中旬喺屈臣氏分店及電子商店公開發售！記得密切留意喇！<br />\n<br />\n$79.9/30個，易賞錢會員優惠價$69.9"},{"pid":"407fdc6c236a9f8b1a38bb96ae0d5283dbd42fe9","tid":2000651,"uid":164435,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:24:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZ1RTwh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZ1RTwh.jpg&h=ffd4a67e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2228b7b064501afbf9e352b15483ec0be7fdbb87","tid":2000651,"uid":321977,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:26:11.000Z","msg":"想睇炒罩狗跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b308cf8f0f6ee9d58e2309351d25cb97f71cd1","tid":2000651,"uid":337826,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:26:48.000Z","msg":"誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17cd833510f77b0bf0b17db7275c9ef1f6378b81","tid":2000651,"uid":21545,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:27:00.000Z","msg":"紙袋仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f66079426c4dc56c4346a86d0dac2385b4b2bfb","tid":2000651,"uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2228b7b064501afbf9e352b154